msgstr "[[!meta title=\"Tails llança un concurs de logotips\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!tag announce]]\n"
msgstr "[[!tag announce]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"On the 29th of April, we will release Tails 1.0. This will be an important "
"symbolic milestone about 5 years after our [[first public releases|news/"
"version_0.2]]."
msgstr ""
"El 29 d'abril llançarem Tails 1.0. Aquesta serà una fita simbòlica important "
"uns 5 anys després de les nostres [[primeres publicacions públiques|news/"
"version_0.2]]."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"We want to have a great logo by then to give Tails the visual impact it "
"deserves. The image and banner we have been using so far don't really do the "
"job anymore..."
msgstr ""
"Volem tenir un gran logotip per llavors per donar a Tails l'impacte visual "
"que es mereix. La imatge i el baner que hem estat utilitzant fins ara ja no "
"fan la feina…"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "<img src=\"https://gitlab.tails.boum.org/tails/blueprints/-/wikis/logo/tails-logo-round.png\" width=\"250\"/>\n"
msgstr ""
"<img src=\"https://gitlab.tails.boum.org/tails/blueprints/-/wikis/logo/tails-"
"logo-round.png\" width=\"250\"/>\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"So we're starting a contest for designers to create a logo for Tails.  We "
"have already brainstormed on the idea, and received some great proposals [[!"
"tails_ticket 5797 desc=\"in the past\"]]. Still, we had a hard time making "
"our collective mind on a single proposal, and wanted to give more people a "
"chance."
msgstr ""
"Així que estem començant un concurs per a dissenyadors per crear un logotip "
"per a Tails. Ja vam fer una pluja d'idees sobre el que volíem i vam rebre "
"algunes [[!tails_ticket 5797 desc=\"propostes fantàstiques\"]]. Tot i així, "
"ens ha costat decidir una única proposta i volíem donar una oportunitat a "
"més gent."

#. type: Plain text
